import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const ReadOnlyRow = ({ user, setDeleteUserId, setEditFormData }) => { const [time, setTime] = useState('') useEffect(() => { setTime(user.createdAt.slice(0, 10)) }, []) return ( <>
{`${user.firstName} ${user.lastName}`} {user.email} {user.role} {time} ) } export default ReadOnlyRow
